        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>The hardest part of any problem is properly defining the problem. The solution is the easy part. The purpose of these rants is to supply as many people as possible with access to information to improve health, wellness, and longevity.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>This intended audience leans toward beginners, novices, and deconditioned individuals</li>
            <li>Dietary focus will be on vegan and plant-based nutrition options</li>
            <li>No advice given here consitiutes a patient-client relationship</li>
